cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.CY, cs.SI 

The paper deals with attacks and defenses related to website fingerprinting, which is a subfield of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also heavily relies on deep learning techniques (cs.LG) and network infrastructure (cs.NI) to carry out the attacks and defenses. Additionally, the paper discusses privacy concerns (cs.CY) and proposes a new countermeasure (cs.SI) to protect against website fingerprinting attacks.
